Package org.jets3t.apps.cockpit.gui

Provides the main GUI components (dialogs and panels) for Cockpit.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AccessControlDialog Dialog for managing S3 access control settings for buckets and objects.
AWSCredentialsDialog Dialog box for obtaining a user's AWS Credentials, where the dialog is simply a wrapping for a LoginCredentialsPanel.
BucketLoggingDialog Dialog box for displaying and modifying the logging status of buckets.
BucketTableModel A table model to store S3Buckets.
ItemPropertiesDialog Dialog to display detailed information about an S3Bucket or a set of S3Objects.
LoginCredentialsPanel A panel for obtaining a user's AWS Credentials.
LoginLocalFolderPanel A panel for displaying a user's login credentials where those credentials are stored in files available on the user's computer.
LoginPassphrasePanel A panel for prompting a user to provide a passphrase and password used to store or access their AWS credentials in S3.
ObjectTableModel A table model to store S3Objects.
PreferencesDialog Dialog box for managing Cockpit Preferences.
ProgressDisplay Class that displays and controls a dialog that shows progress information to the user for long-lived tasks.
StartupDialog Dialog box for obtaining a user's AWS Credentials, and performing other startup tasks such as loading properties files.
 

Package org.jets3t.apps.cockpit.gui Description

Provides the main GUI components (dialogs and panels) for Cockpit.
